dct_title_s: Brookwood, Jackson Township, New Jersey 1962 section 3A
dct_description_sm: Map of Brookwood, Section 3A, Jackson Township, Ocean County, N.J. along with inset map of township. Map features a table of curve data and official approvals and signatures from various county planning board and civil engineering officials.
